			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">碎石原体蓄力，发射一枚石弹，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
