				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">碎石原体进行一段挥扫攻击，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">碎石原体进入「应激」状态，该状态下，狂蔓原体将获得<span textDecoration="underline">坚岩护嶂</span><span>，持续进行大范围石潮舞击，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害，持续4轮。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
